## 8. Example: Full CRUD Flow

```js
// CREATE
const id = ScoreboardStorage.save("items_db", {
    itemId: "diamond_sword",
    durability: 1561,
    owner: "Steve"
});

// READ
const item = ScoreboardStorage.getById("items_db", id);

// UPDATE
ScoreboardStorage.updateById("items_db", id, {
    itemId: "diamond_sword",
    durability: 1200,
    owner: "Steve"
});

// DELETE
ScoreboardStorage.deleteById("items_db", id);
```

